WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:01.129
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.129 --> 00:00:05.663
I have a very strong prophetic warning to give right now.

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:12.020
Last night I was praying, and in my prayer time, the Lord opened my eyes to the spirit realm.

00:00:12.315 --> 00:00:17.370
He said, "Brandon, the last visions have come and they've gone.

00:00:17.370 --> 00:00:22.587
" What the Lord showed me about New Orleans and Las Vegas has happened.

00:00:22.587 --> 00:00:29.160
So now He said, "I'm going to show you the next wave of things that you are to warn the body for what is coming.

00:00:30.240 --> 00:01:18.622
" It all started while I was just worshipping and praying like I normally do, and all of a sudden, it was as if a vision was being put out in front of me.

00:01:19.173 --> 00:01:37.074
I told my wife, "Get the phone, you've got to record it.

00:01:52.880 --> 00:02:07.200
" I saw massive farming equipment on the East Coast, and there were silos.

00:02:10.410 --> 00:02:30.559
The Lord said, "I want you to focus on fertilizer.

00:02:30.559 --> 00:02:54.903
" All of a sudden, everything was coming at me very fast.

00:02:54.903 --> 00:03:33.420
I could see these men buying lots of fertilizer since this summer over the course of quite a while.

00:03:38.235 --> 00:04:38.444
I have to describe what I saw: I saw trees with leaves, summer grass growing—it was hot outside—and I saw these men collecting fertilizer through different places so that they would not be detected, buying in bulk without drawing suspicion.

00:04:38.444 --> 00:04:50.070
These men were storing this fertilizer.

00:05:00.836 --> 00:05:37.886
I saw massive dump trucks with separation in the back containing 50-gallon drums filled with different chemicals to make what happened in Oklahoma City back in the '90s.

00:05:37.886 --> 00:06:17.120
This was not black powder, but this fertilizer stuff in a big diesel dump truck that looked like a construction vehicle.

00:06:22.977 --> 00:06:50.504
They put all this in so that it would cause a major catastrophic event.

00:06:56.199 --> 00:07:41.248
They made the front of it bulletproof with very strong armor so you could not shoot it to stop it.

00:07:41.248 --> 00:07:57.546
This armor was underneath, so it wasn't easily seen.

00:08:10.507 --> 00:08:39.366
I saw these men with vests on in the front cab of the truck, and they had explosives on these vests.

00:08:39.366 --> 00:09:17.480
There were two men in the truck, and they used it to go through police and military barricades in Washington, D.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:19.280
C.

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:59.366
When they tried to stop them at a checkpoint, they pushed through the barricade because the truck was very strong.

00:09:59.366 --> 00:10:24.040
Then they were surrounded, they ignited their vests, and they took out everybody.

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:52.733
When this happened, there was a massive crater in the ground and all the buildings were completely wiped out.

00:10:52.733 --> 00:11:19.290
They tried to get as close as they could to the Capitol and major landmarks of Washington, D.

00:11:19.290 --> 00:11:20.990
C.

00:11:20.990 --> 00:11:41.250
The Lord spoke to me about lone wolves in America.

00:11:41.250 --> 00:11:49.297
They were sympathetic to terrorism, acting alone.

00:11:49.297 --> 00:12:19.256
They are part of an organization, but they are not part of a big group.

00:12:20.408 --> 00:12:29.239
I saw different individuals throughout towns acting alone.

00:12:29.239 --> 00:12:56.476
There were lots of them, and they weren't necessarily illegal immigrants from across the border; they were people who already lived here.

00:13:02.813 --> 00:13:23.022
The Lord showed me white cargo vans with no windows on the side that would carry 50-gallon drums of fertilizer.

00:13:23.022 --> 00:13:49.320
They were parking them in New York City in parking garages and close to buildings so they did not look suspicious.

00:13:49.657 --> 00:14:41.000
I saw them trying to get as close as they could to Trump Towers, and they had a plan to take out Trump Towers and golf courses throughout America.

00:14:42.142 --> 00:14:56.600
The Lord spoke to me and said, "This is bigger than terrorists.

00:14:56.600 --> 00:15:21.543
" I saw it was in retaliation for Qasem Soleimani, the man that was taken out in Iraq.

00:15:30.926 --> 00:15:42.213
I saw that man's face, and they said, "We have not forgotten his assassination.

00:15:53.834 --> 00:15:59.234
" They were coming against America, especially Trump, in retaliation for what happened in Iran.

00:16:03.445 --> 00:16:23.480
I saw this was a government operation with a thousand men coming through underground drug trafficking tunnels.

00:16:23.480 --> 00:16:53.319
This is a multi-hundred-million-dollar operation that has been going on for the last four years, gathering supplies, and they are here.

00:17:04.460 --> 00:17:26.034
I saw darkness in ten major cities, with groups of a hundred people per attack coming out of the ground like ants.

00:17:32.937 --> 00:17:49.600
The Lord said, "This is not terrorists per se; this is an act of war.

00:17:49.600 --> 00:18:12.220
" This is a government of another country coming against America, making it look like terrorism.

00:18:25.760 --> 00:18:40.263
You will see a great shaking still to come because of past administrations not securing the borders.

00:18:43.070 --> 00:18:59.559
I warn you to pray—not a call to fear, but a call to prayer.

00:19:04.840 --> 00:19:21.309
I saw plans and plots from these men to try to disrupt the inauguration.

00:19:21.309 --> 00:19:34.279
After the election, I heard the word "strike" five times.

00:19:34.279 --> 00:19:57.440
These were major events trying to bring fear upon the American people.

00:19:57.440 --> 00:20:13.300
We must pray for what is dear to Trump, specifically his children.

00:20:15.937 --> 00:20:32.573
This is about retaliation, with funding hidden through crypto and communication through untraceable sources.

00:20:46.378 --> 00:20:52.182
It is about Syria and things happening as America lines up with Israel.

00:20:53.053 --> 00:21:16.919
We pray protection over your families, our President, and the capital of America.

00:21:16.919 --> 00:21:41.340
This was very dark; these people obviously do not value their own lives.

00:21:41.340 --> 00:22:01.520
When they ignited their vests, it was a massive explosion, bigger than Oklahoma City.

00:22:01.520 --> 00:22:25.867
It was fertilizer, and I am trying to communicate what I see in the spirit.

00:22:25.867 --> 00:22:40.536
These vans were targeted at Trump hotels and locations.

00:22:40.536 --> 00:22:59.120
It is a network of people who want to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:22:59.120 --> 00:23:11.765
It was also about Europe, including France and England.

00:23:14.464 --> 00:23:58.600
I am not here to stir up fear, but the last visions I saw came to pass, and now the Lord is giving more.

00:24:04.845 --> 00:24:16.817
I believe we lessened what happened in New Orleans by prayer.

00:24:25.899 --> 00:24:48.194
In Las Vegas, God used a bulletproof Cybertruck to shoot the blast straight up, so the glass at the Trump building did not even break.

00:24:48.194 --> 00:24:56.880
Even the tires were not popped.

00:24:56.880 --> 00:25:34.000
While people lost their lives in New Orleans, where there is a strong presence of witchcraft on Bourbon Street, we can stop these events through prayer.

00:25:34.000 --> 00:26:03.507
My job is to raise up a million-person prayer army to change events in politics and the financial realm.

00:26:03.507 --> 00:26:20.159
It is time to rise and shine, for the light has come.

00:26:24.325 --> 00:26:44.559
You have the ability to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt you.

00:26:44.559 --> 00:27:21.120
He gave His angels charge to bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:27:21.120 --> 00:27:37.950
It is time for the body of Christ to take our authority.

00:27:37.950 --> 00:27:48.980
I believe we will see great changes.

00:27:48.980 --> 00:28:04.045
New Orleans was tragic, but it could have been worse.

00:28:04.045 --> 00:28:20.393
Pipe bombs did not go off and churches were not affected.

00:28:20.393 --> 00:28:46.650
This will be a year of great acceleration and an outpouring of the Spirit.

00:28:58.648 --> 00:29:14.093
I talked to an elderly Jewish man about the tradition of the groom giving presents to the bride.

00:29:14.093 --> 00:29:34.460
He said that was an old tradition, and that is what Jesus would go by.

00:29:34.460 --> 00:29:56.919
God is giving His remnant gifts, and huge financial blessings are coming to the church.

00:29:56.919 --> 00:30:04.725
In 2025, believe for big things.

00:30:04.725 --> 00:30:24.360
I am believing for my daughter's healing and for God to show up in our lives.

00:30:24.360 --> 00:30:56.760
As a watchman, I am looking through my binoculars again and seeing another major event, but we can stop and lessen this through prayer.

00:30:57.530 --> 00:31:21.170
We pray for supernatural protection over the Secret Service assigned to Trump, that the Holy Spirit would reveal danger to them.

00:31:21.170 --> 00:31:36.311
Father, I thank You for this country and for President Trump.

00:31:43.059 --> 00:31:52.711
I thank You for the wisdom given to the administration to stop these hidden cells.

00:32:00.520 --> 00:32:02.880
We pray for confusion in the enemy's camp.

00:32:02.880 --> 00:32:28.977
America is a giver; we have sowed billions to Ukraine and Israel, and whatsoever a man sows, he shall reap.

00:32:31.178 --> 00:32:45.639
We pray for mercy and that You would heal our land.

00:32:48.999 --> 00:33:19.979
We thank You that these men are brought to justice in all ten cities and at every Trump location.

00:33:19.979 --> 00:33:56.663
We pray a hedge of protection around landmarks like the New York Stock Exchange and the One World Trade Center.

00:34:18.610 --> 00:35:45.500
We pray for mending hearts in New Orleans and the restoration of all that was lost.

00:35:45.500 --> 00:35:57.005
I thank You, Lord, for restoring what the cankerworm ate ate in these people's lives.

00:35:59.240 --> 00:36:35.040
We thank You for the supernatural finances pouring out on the remnant.

00:36:54.935 --> 00:37:54.067
You are the God of Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego, and You will protect us from the fiery furnace and the lions' den.

00:37:59.600 --> 00:38:22.608
A thousand may fall at our side, but it will not come near us.

00:38:34.159 --> 00:39:02.115
We thank You for the anointing of the Holy Spirit and Your grace and mercy.

00:39:05.184 --> 00:39:44.599
We call everyone healed and delivered from sickness, dementia, Alzheimer's, depression, or anxiety.

00:39:45.760 --> 00:40:26.611
We receive Your divine protection in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:40:26.611 --> 00:40:29.970
Amen.

00:40:29.970 --> 00:40:34.550
I hope this video blessed you.

00:40:34.550 --> 00:41:03.839
I have to tell you what I saw so the government can prepare.

00:41:03.839 --> 00:41:31.337
They have been buying fertilizer in small amounts over time to avoid attention.

00:41:31.337 --> 00:42:05.550
The enemy is coming down, but the Lord shows us this so we can pray against it.

00:42:05.550 --> 00:42:15.120
We take communion for divine protection.

00:42:15.120 --> 00:42:23.760
By Your stripes, we are healed.

00:42:24.510 --> 00:43:01.853
We are overcomers by the blood of the Lamb and the word of our testimony.

00:43:01.853 --> 00:44:31.354
God has not given you a spirit of fear but of power, love, and a sound mind.

00:44:31.354 --> 00:45:11.326
Where the blood is applied, Satan cannot cross.

00:45:11.326 --> 00:46:08.640
We apply the blood over our towns and cities.

00:46:08.640 --> 00:46:49.190
We surrender all to You, our blessed Savior.

00:46:49.200 --> 00:47:29.702
Great is Your faithfulness to us, oh God.

00:47:29.702 --> 00:47:43.504
Holy Spirit, thou art welcome in this place.

00:47:43.504 --> 00:48:08.547
Omnipotent Father of mercy and grace, thou art welcome in this place.

00:48:12.178 --> 00:48:23.239
In Your presence, there is healing divine.

00:48:23.239 --> 00:48:46.097
Hallelujah, You have won the victory and given it all for me.

00:48:46.097 --> 00:49:10.610
Death could not hold You down; You are the Risen King, seated in majesty.

00:49:21.005 --> 00:49:26.989
We refresh today as we drink from the living water.

00:49:26.989 --> 00:49:36.466
Jesus is coming soon.

00:49:36.466 --> 00:49:52.330
Thank you for joining us in prayer.

00:50:01.690 --> 00:50:07.354
We pray for your supernatural breakthrough in 2025.

00:50:07.354 --> 00:50:49.776
We cry out like blind Bartimaeus, "Jesus, Son of David, have mercy on us!

00:51:40.144 --> 00:51:54.540
" We are Your joint-heirs, and we are seated with You at the table.

00:51:54.540 --> 00:52:24.339
Come and dine, for He turned the water into wine.

00:52:24.339 --> 00:52:44.915
Peace, wonderful peace, coming down from the Father above.
